These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, scientist
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, handball
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, motorbike
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the fisherman is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing       | puzzles |
| Job         | scientist | fisherman  |
| Sport       | handball    | biathlon    |
| Transport   | motorbike       | train      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, nurse
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, comedy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, rowing
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the journalist is on the far left##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | milk |
| Job           | journalist | nurse      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | mystery      |
| Sport         | skateboarding | rowing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk
There 2 different types of food: carrot, cabbage
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, salsa
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, trike
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk  |
| Food          | carrot    | cabbage   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | dubstep   |
| Transport     | trike     | ship |

 #################################

 
