.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, project-manager
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, fantasy
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, subway
1. the doctor is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the doctor is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | project-manager | doctor     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery          | fantasy |
| Pet           | chinchilla          | rat    |
| Transport     | subway            | taxi       |

 